OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782132502
OL,3,CGirl and two boys arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of teenager's murder
OL,6,FThree teenagers have been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a 17-year-
OL,8,Fold boy was killed in a suspected
OL,9,Fstabbing in south-west London.
OL,11,FIt comes after the death of Jamal
OL,12,FCoombes, in Battersea, in the early
OL,13,Fhours of Saturday.
OL,15,FA boy and a girl, both aged 15, were
OL,16,Farrested on Saturday and a 14-year-old
OL,17,Fboy was arrested on Sunday, the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police said. They all
OL,19,Fremain in custody.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
