OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782132502
OL,3,CGirl and two boys arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of teenager's murder
OL,6,FOfficers were called to Glycena Road,
OL,7,FBattersea, at 4.20am and found Jamal
OL,8,Fseriously injured.
OL,10,FThe London Ambulance Service and
OL,11,FLondon's Air Ambulance attended but
OL,12,Fdespite the efforts of paramedics, he
OL,13,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,15,FPolice believe there was an
OL,16,Faltercation prior to the assault and
OL,17,Fthey have appealed for information
OL,18,Ffrom anyone who "witnessed a group of
OL,19,Fmen running" to come forward.
OL,26,@zD@QOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
