CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782132502
OL,3,CGirl and two boys arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of teenager's murder
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Brian Howie,
OL,7,Fthe senior investigating officer
OL,8,Fleading the inquiry for the Met's
OL,9,FSpecialist Crime Command, said: "Our
OL,10,Fthoughts remain firmly with Jamal's
OL,11,Floved ones following his tragic death.
OL,13,F"I understand the impact this incident
OL,14,Fhas had on the local community.
OL,16,F"If you have any questions or
OL,17,Fconcerns, do not hesitate to speak
OL,18,Fwith one of our officers on patrol in
OL,19,Fthe area this week.
OL,26,@qD@aOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782132502
OL,3,CGirl and two boys arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of teenager's murder
OL,6,F"As our inquiries continue, I am
OL,7,Fappealing directly to the public.
OL,9,F"We believe that there was an
OL,10,Faltercation prior to the assault."
OL,12,FHe said detectives are looking for
OL,13,Fanyone who was in the Lavender Hill
OL,14,Farea between 3.30am and 5am in Glycena
OL,15,FRoad, Acanthus Road or Pountney Road,
OL,16,Fand "witnessed a group of men running".
OL,18,FHe added: "Any information, no matter
OL,19,Fhow minor it may seem, could prove
OL,20,Fcrucial.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUrD@bO]xD@EOUxD@fO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
