OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782132502
OL,3,CGirl and two boys arrested on
OL,4,Csuspicion of teenager's murder
OL,6,F"CCTV, doorbell or mobile phone
OL,7,Ffootage may provide vital evidence.
OL,9,F"I would also urge members of the
OL,10,Fpublic not to assume that information
OL,11,Fhas already been shared, any detail
OL,12,Fcould be of significant importance to
OL,13,Fthe investigation."
OL,15,FAnyone with information or footage can
OL,16,Fcontact police on 101, quoting CAD
OL,17,F1567/20JUN26.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@SO]
